  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a copper mug over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, and cayenne pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced melon and chopped pickle and cook until the melon is tender.",
    "Stir in the plain yogurt and cook until the mixture is heated through.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the tagine for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
